title.rendered: BOSS AIR TYRE INFLATOR/DEFLATOR PORTABLE COMPRESSOR

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR TYRE INFLATOR/DEFLATOR PORTABLE COMPRESSOR

Boss Air Tyre Inflator/Deflator Portable Compressor available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This little compact compressor pumps up to 100PSI and is the perfect tyre checker/inflator AND deflater.

Key features include;

  • Tyre gauge for easy reading
  • Unique tyre deflator button.
  • Cigarette lighter attachment
  • Inflation accessories.
  • Convenient Carry Case

Specs:

  • Voltage 12 Volt DC
  • Weight 1 KG
  • Max Amps 15 Amps
  • Max Working pressure 100 PSI
  • Cord length 3 metres
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
